18.Nc3 White will regain his pawn with a clear advantage, as with 18...Bd3 18..
.d5 ? 19.Nxe4 exploits Black's uncoordinated pieces 19.Nxe4 Bxe4 20.Bxe4 when
the white bishop is clearly superior to the knight. White might follow up with
