g4 Nxg4 ? 14.hxg4 Bxg4 15.f3 Bh3 16.Ng3 keeps control. Or just 13.Nxf6+ Bxf6
14.g4 ! Bg6 15.Ng3 was the way to maintain control. White will play to make
