18.Qe3 Qa5 19.Nd5 would also have been pretty strong.} Bc6 18. b4 {Simon is
happy to seize space right across the board.} b5 {A common reaction in such
positions, but rarely a good one. Black needed to dig in with 18...b6 when 19.
Rc1 a5 20.b5 Bb7 21.Qd2 favours White, despite his fixed pawns on the
